<br>
54 Shield of Magi- 24 MR<br>
54 Elemental Cloak- 45 CR 45 FR<br>
49 Shield of Lava- 25 FR (short lived, I admit)<br>
49 Elemental Blanket- 15 MR 15 CR 15 FR<br>
39 Dagger of Symbols- 5 MR 5 PR 5 DR<br>
34 Shard of Core- 15 CR 15 PR<br>
<br>
Total:  44 MR, 75 CR, 85 FR, 20 PR, 5 DR<br>
<br>
For self buffing (at the cost of a few prime slots) we can do pretty good.  Toss in the various cleric / druid / enchanter buffs and we can resist quite a lot.<br>
<br>
